  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click, Drag, and Drop shapes onto each other to merge them! A relaxing physics-based shape merging game. Play with a variety of colorful shapes in a limited play area with this simple yet addicting puzzle game. Get the highest score you can, but be careful! Don't let the stack of shapes get too high, or its game over!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/6a2bdf58af27529b06e4453989c6444b.poster.avif?t=1770533586\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/6a2bdf58af27529b06e4453989c6444b.webm?t=1770533586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/6a2bdf58af27529b06e4453989c6444b.mp4?t=1770533586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-Player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple click and drag mechanics.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let go of the mouse to drop the shape.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like shapes will merge together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shapes are physics based and will fall when dropped.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewarding visuals and relaxing sounds to juice up the player experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine the biggest shapes for a large reward and to clear much of the play areas space.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/c5184eef622d7a01ed838bf1572b9c5a.poster.avif?t=1770533586\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/c5184eef622d7a01ed838bf1572b9c5a.webm?t=1770533586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/c5184eef622d7a01ed838bf1572b9c5a.mp4?t=1770533586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a great way to burn through time or to give your mind something relaxing to do. If you're competitive see if your friends can get a higher score than you. Else, sit back, relax, and drop some shapes!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click, Drag, and Drop shapes onto each other to merge them! A relaxing physics-based shape merging game. Play with a variety of colorful shapes in a limited play area with this simple yet addicting puzzle game. Get the highest score you can, but be careful! Don't let the stack of shapes get too high, or its game over!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/6a2bdf58af27529b06e4453989c6444b.poster.avif?t=1770533586\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/6a2bdf58af27529b06e4453989c6444b.webm?t=1770533586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/6a2bdf58af27529b06e4453989c6444b.mp4?t=1770533586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-Player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple click and drag mechanics.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let go of the mouse to drop the shape.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like shapes will merge together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shapes are physics based and will fall when dropped.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewarding visuals and relaxing sounds to juice up the player experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine the biggest shapes for a large reward and to clear much of the play areas space.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/c5184eef622d7a01ed838bf1572b9c5a.poster.avif?t=1770533586\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/c5184eef622d7a01ed838bf1572b9c5a.webm?t=1770533586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3604070/extras/c5184eef622d7a01ed838bf1572b9c5a.mp4?t=1770533586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a great way to burn through time or to give your mind something relaxing to do. If you're competitive see if your friends can get a higher score than you. Else, sit back, relax, and drop some shapes!</p>",
